# CONTOH KONFIGURASI - Copy ke .env Anda

# ============================================
# WHATSAPP CONFIGURATION
# ============================================

# STEP 1: Set ke true untuk aktifkan
WHATSAPP_ENABLED=true

# STEP 2: Pilih provider (fonnte, wablas, atau twilio)
WHATSAPP_PROVIDER=fonnte

# STEP 3: API URL sesuai provider
# Fonnte:
WHATSAPP_API_URL=https://api.fonnte.com

# Wablas (jika pakai Wablas):
# WHATSAPP_API_URL=https://xxxx.wablas.com

# STEP 4: Paste API Token Anda dari dashboard provider
# Contoh token Fonnte (GANTI dengan token Anda):
WHATSAPP_API_TOKEN=abc123xyz456def789ghi012jkl345mno678pqr901stu234

# STEP 5: Nomor WhatsApp pengirim (format 628xxx)
WHATSAPP_SENDER=6288991144184

# ============================================
# CARA DAPAT API TOKEN:
# ============================================
#
# FONNTE:
# 1. Daftar di https://fonnte.com
# 2. Verifikasi email
# 3. Login ke dashboard
# 4. Scan QR Code dengan HP WhatsApp
# 5. Copy API Token yang muncul di dashboard
#
# WABLAS:
# 1. Daftar di https://wablas.com
# 2. Verifikasi akun
# 3. Login ke member area
# 4. Generate device
# 5. Scan QR Code
# 6. Copy API Token
#
# ============================================
# TEST SETUP:
# ============================================
# 
# Setelah setup:
# 1. php artisan config:clear
# 2. php artisan serve
# 3. Login ke admin
# 4. Menu: PSB → Notifikasi
# 5. Klik "Test Koneksi WhatsApp"
# 6. Jika sukses, siap pakai!
#
# ============================================
